What do you get when you run these 3 test ROMs in order? <a href="http://h1.ripway.com/blargg/temp/apu_irq_flag.zip" class="postlink">apu_irq_flag.zip</a><br /><br />Here's the relevant code for 07.irq_flag_timing.nes:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">set_test 2,&quot;Flag first set too soon&quot;<br />jsr sync_apu<br />lda #$00        ; begin mode 0<br />sta $4017<br />delay 29826<br />lda $4015       ; at 29830 flag should be clear<br />and #$40<br />jne test_failed<br /><br />set_test 3,&quot;Flag first set too late&quot;<br />jsr sync_apu<br />lda #$00        ; begin mode 0<br />sta $4017<br />delay 29827<br />lda $4015       ; at 29831 flag should be set<br />and #$40<br />jeq test_failed<br /><br />set_test 4,&quot;Flag last set too soon&quot;<br />jsr sync_apu<br />lda #$00        ; begin mode 0<br />sta $4017<br />delay 29828<br />lda $4015       ; at 29832 read and clear flag<br />lda $4015       ; flag should be set again<br />and #$40<br />jeq test_failed<br /><br />set_test 5,&quot;Flag last set too late &quot;<br />jsr sync_apu<br />lda #$00        ; begin mode 0<br />sta $4017<br />delay 29829<br />lda $4015       ; at 29833 read and clear flag<br />lda $4015       ; flag should't be set again<br />and #$40<br />jne test_failed</div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=17">blargg</a> — Fri Feb 22, 2008 4:21 pm</p><hr />
